snippet.title: Densha de Go! Professional (PC)
snippet.description:
"Professional" meaning the harder, more challenging version of the game. This installment in the Densha de Go! series includes many routes for you to drive. In my opinion, being one of the best versions in the series due to that. 

This game was released in 2004 for Windows computers by Japanese publisher UNBALANCE.

I was doing pretty good in the beginning, until the game screwed me over and made me go super slow – ultimately, ending up falling behind schedule. Oh well, though. 

2015 is almost over!
